     =========================================================
     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================

                            Test01
                            ----------

  The purpose of this test is to exercise the CSG as well as boolean solids 
  extensively using the full apparatus of the G4 geometry. It also exicises
  assemblies with different configurations (simple,  assembly of assemblies
  and containing reflections).

  Author: Vladimir Grichine
  Contributors: Simone Giani, John Apostolakis, Gabriele Cosmo,
                Radovan Chytracek, Ivana Hrivnacova.

  To run it you can use

    test01 *.in or *.mac
